\'97\'97\'97\
\ul ISO 3 Countries and Time series\
\ulnone In each sheet, the data are organized per country (rows) and year (columns), with their respective value in the headers. Country name is the ISO3 3-letter acronym.\
Emissions are annual from 1996 to 2013 (note: there\'92s a 1995 column, but it\'92s all zeros).\
\
\'97 \'97 \'97 \
\ul Units\
\ulnone All emission data are provided as 
\b Tons emitted per country per year
